tpt_misc_notify.name: tpt_misc_notify

revisions.description: Updated copyright information. Minor MIB syntax fixes.
Added emergency, alert, notice, info, and debug severity values to SystemLogSeverity.
Added SSL inspected flag parameter to quarantine notifications.
Added audit log notification and objects.

tptMiscNotifyDeviceID.name: tptMiscNotifyDeviceID
tptMiscNotifyDeviceID.description: The unique identifier of the device sending this notification.

tptManagedNotify.name: tptManagedNotify
tptManagedNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that the device is now being managed by said management station.

tptUnmanagedNotify.name: tptUnmanagedNotify
tptUnmanagedNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that the device is no longer being managed by said management station.

LogFileType.name: LogFileType
LogFileType.description: The type of the file that has rolled over.

tptRolloverNotifyFileType.name: tptRolloverNotifyFileType
tptRolloverNotifyFileType.description: The type of the file that has rolled over.

tptRolloverNotifyMaxFiles.name: tptRolloverNotifyMaxFiles
tptRolloverNotifyMaxFiles.description: The maximum number of files maintained for this log file type.

tptRolloverNotifyNumFiles.name: tptRolloverNotifyNumFiles
tptRolloverNotifyNumFiles.description: The number of files that have rolled over.

tptRolloverNotifyTime.name: tptRolloverNotifyTime
tptRolloverNotifyTime.description: The rollover time of the most recent file pertaining to this notification (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

tptRolloverNotify.name: tptRolloverNotify
tptRolloverNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a log file has rolled over.

DiscoveryDelta.name: DiscoveryDelta
DiscoveryDelta.description: An indication of whether discovery results changed from the previous scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyScanID.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyScanID
tptDiscoveryNotifyScanID.description: The unique identifier of the scan pertaining to this notification.

tptDiscoveryNotifySegmentName.name: tptDiscoveryNotifySegmentName
tptDiscoveryNotifySegmentName.description: The name of the scanned segment pertaining to this notification.

tptDiscoveryNotifyScanRange.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyScanRange
tptDiscoveryNotifyScanRange.description: The network address range requested in the scan pertaining to this notification.

tptDiscoveryNotifyDelta.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyDelta
tptDiscoveryNotifyDelta.description: An indication of whether discovery results changed from the previous scan. Undefined if this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyNewHosts.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyNewHosts
tptDiscoveryNotifyNewHosts.description: The number of new hosts found by this scan (compared to the previous scan). Undefined if this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyChanged.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyChanged
tptDiscoveryNotifyChanged.description: The number of hosts for which this scan found different results from the previous scan. Undefined if this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyUnchanged.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyUnchanged
tptDiscoveryNotifyUnchanged.description: The number of existing hosts for which this scan found the same results (compared to the previous scan). Undefined if this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyNotFound.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyNotFound
tptDiscoveryNotifyNotFound.description: The number of hosts found by the previous scan but not by this scan. Undefined if this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyUnknown.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyUnknown
tptDiscoveryNotifyUnknown.description: The number of addresses scanned where no host was found and for which there was no previous scan data. Undefined if this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyStartTime.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyStartTime
tptDiscoveryNotifyStartTime.description: The start time of the scan pertaining to this notification (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

tptDiscoveryNotifyStopTime.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyStopTime
tptDiscoveryNotifyStopTime.description: The stop time of the scan pertaining to this notification (in seconds since January 1, 1970). A zero value indicates that this notification signifies the start of a scan.

tptDiscoveryNotifyErrorText.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyErrorText
tptDiscoveryNotifyErrorText.description: If the current scan terminated abnormally, this string describes the error condition. Otherwise, an empty string.

tptDiscoveryNotifySchedID.name: tptDiscoveryNotifySchedID
tptDiscoveryNotifySchedID.description: For a notification resulting from a scheduled scan, this value holds the scheduled scan identifier. Otherwise, this value is undefined.

tptDiscoveryNotifyStartStop.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyStartStop
tptDiscoveryNotifyStartStop.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a network discovery scan has started or stopped.

tptDiscoveryNotifyHostNetAddr.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyHostNetAddr
tptDiscoveryNotifyHostNetAddr.description: The network address of the newly discovered host.

tptDiscoveryNotifyHostDeviceID.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyHostDeviceID
tptDiscoveryNotifyHostDeviceID.description: The unique identifier of the newly discovered host.

tptDiscoveryNotifyNewHost.name: tptDiscoveryNotifyNewHost
tptDiscoveryNotifyNewHost.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a previously unknown host was discovered by a scan.

SystemLogSeverity.name: SystemLogSeverity
SystemLogSeverity.description: An indication of the severity of a system log message.

tptSystemLogNotifyText.name: tptSystemLogNotifyText
tptSystemLogNotifyText.description: The text of the message being logged.

tptSystemLogNotifySequence.name: tptSystemLogNotifySequence
tptSystemLogNotifySequence.description: The log file entry sequence number corresponding to this notification.

tptSystemLogNotifySeverity.name: tptSystemLogNotifySeverity
tptSystemLogNotifySeverity.description: The severity of the attack for this notification.

tptSystemLogNotifyTimeSec.name: tptSystemLogNotifyTimeSec
tptSystemLogNotifyTimeSec.description: The time this message was logged (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

tptSystemLogNotify.name: tptSystemLogNotify
tptSystemLogNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a critical, error, or warning message has been logged.

AddOrRemove.name: AddOrRemove
AddOrRemove.description: An indication of whether a host was added to or removed from the quarantine list.

tptQuarantineNotifyHostNetAddr.name: tptQuarantineNotifyHostNetAddr
tptQuarantineNotifyHostNetAddr.description: The network address of the host being quarantined (or removed).

tptQuarantineNotifyHostNetAddrV6.name: tptQuarantineNotifyHostNetAddrV6
tptQuarantineNotifyHostNetAddrV6.description: The IPv6 network address of the host being quarantined (or removed).

tptQuarantineNotifyReason.name: tptQuarantineNotifyReason
tptQuarantineNotifyReason.description: The reason that a host was quarantined (undefined if action is remove).

tptQuarantineNotifySegmentName.name: tptQuarantineNotifySegmentName
tptQuarantineNotifySegmentName.description: A string of the format <slot>:<index> that uniquely identifies the segment pertaining to this notification.

tptQuarantineNotifyAction.name: tptQuarantineNotifyAction
tptQuarantineNotifyAction.description: Whether the host was added to or removed from the quarantine list.

tptQuarantineNotifySslInspected.name: tptQuarantineNotifySslInspected
tptQuarantineNotifySslInspected.description: Flag indicating if this quarantine action was performed on an inspected SSL data stream.

tptQuarantineNotify.name: tptQuarantineNotify
tptQuarantineNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a host has been either added to or removed from the quarantine list.

CongestionThresholdPhase.name: CongestionThresholdPhase
CongestionThresholdPhase.description: The congestion threshold phase (entering, continuing, or exiting).

tptCongestionPacketLoss.name: tptCongestionPacketLoss
tptCongestionPacketLoss.description: The current packet loss rate per thousand (percent * 10).

tptCongestionNotifyPhase.name: tptCongestionNotifyPhase
tptCongestionNotifyPhase.description: Whether entering, continuing, or exiting congestion threshold mode.

tptCongestionThreshold.name: tptCongestionThreshold
tptCongestionThreshold.description: The current packet loss threshold per thousand (percent * 10).

tptTier3CongestionPacketLoss.name: tptTier3CongestionPacketLoss
tptTier3CongestionPacketLoss.description: The current tier3 packet loss rate per thousand (percent * 10).

tptTier3CongestionNotifyPhase.name: tptTier3CongestionNotifyPhase
tptTier3CongestionNotifyPhase.description: Whether entering, continuing, or exiting tier3 congestion threshold mode.

tptTier3CongestionThreshold.name: tptTier3CongestionThreshold
tptTier3CongestionThreshold.description: The current tier3 packet loss threshold per thousand (percent * 10).

tptCongestionThresholdNotify.name: tptCongestionThresholdNotify
tptCongestionThresholdNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that the device-wide congestion has exceeded the configured congestion threshold.

tptiTier3CongestionThresholdNotify.name: tptiTier3CongestionThresholdNotify
tptiTier3CongestionThresholdNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that the tier3 congestion has exceeded the configured congestion threshold.

AuditLogResult.name: AuditLogResult
AuditLogResult.description: The result of an audit check: success, or fail.

AuditLogCategory.name: AuditLogCategory
AuditLogCategory.description: The functional location of where an audit check was made and generated a log entry.

tptAuditLogNotifyTime.name: tptAuditLogNotifyTime
tptAuditLogNotifyTime.description: The date and time when the entry was logged.

tptAuditLogNotifyAccess.name: tptAuditLogNotifyAccess
tptAuditLogNotifyAccess.description: The access level of the user initiating the audit check and generating the log. This is a bit field with the following mapping: 0x0 - normal 0x1 - operator 0x4 - administrator 0x8 - super-user

tptAuditLogNotifyType.name: tptAuditLogNotifyType
tptAuditLogNotifyType.description: The interface source of the audit log action.

tptAuditLogNotifyIpAddrType.name: tptAuditLogNotifyIpAddrType
tptAuditLogNotifyIpAddrType.description: The type of IP address from which the user connected.

tptAuditLogNotifyIpAddr.name: tptAuditLogNotifyIpAddr
tptAuditLogNotifyIpAddr.description: The IP address from which the user connected.

tptAuditLogNotifyCategory.name: tptAuditLogNotifyCategory
tptAuditLogNotifyCategory.description: The functional area where the audit log was generated.

tptAuditLogNotifyResult.name: tptAuditLogNotifyResult
tptAuditLogNotifyResult.description: The result, pass or fail, of an audit check.

tptAuditLogNotifyUser.name: tptAuditLogNotifyUser
tptAuditLogNotifyUser.description: The user initiating the audit check and generating the log.

tptAuditLogNotifyMessage.name: tptAuditLogNotifyMessage
tptAuditLogNotifyMessage.description: A description of what configuration change was attempted (and possibly succeeded) by the user.

tptAuditLogCapacityNotifyPercent.name: tptAuditLogCapacityNotifyPercent
tptAuditLogCapacityNotifyPercent.description: The time of this notification (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

tptAuditLogCapacityOrFailureNotifyTime.name: tptAuditLogCapacityOrFailureNotifyTime
tptAuditLogCapacityOrFailureNotifyTime.description: The time of this notification (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

tptAuditLogCapacityNotify.name: tptAuditLogCapacityNotify
tptAuditLogCapacityNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that audit log file size has reached more than 75 percent.

tptLoggingFailureNotify.name: tptLoggingFailureNotify
tptLoggingFailureNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that logging has failed.
